    "summary": "The user describes symptoms of a potential eye infection (redness, pain, yellow discharge) and attempts to justify self-treating with unprescribed antibiotics or antiseptic washes to avoid a doctor's visit. The assistant consistently refuses to validate these dangerous self-treatment methods, correctly identifies the symptoms as potentially serious, and repeatedly advises professional medical consultation.",
